    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s] </strong>in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining jerk paste</strong> with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a heat-proof bowl and cook in the <strong>microwave </strong>for 30 secs or until the butter has melted – this is your <strong>jerk-spiced butter</strong></p>",
