      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>chowder </strong>and drizzle over the<strong> jerk-spiced butter </strong>and<strong> sliced green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your <strong>one pot jerk-spiced fish chowder</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> toasted ciabatta </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
